headline: Corpay Cross-Border Named the Official FX Partner of New Zealand Football
summary: TORONTO, August 20, 2025--Corpay, Inc.*, (NYSE: CPAY) a global leader in corporate payments, is pleased to announce that Corpay’s Cross-Border business has entered into an agreement with New Zealand Football to become their Official Foreign Exchange (FX) Partner.
